    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "model_arch_text",
      "x": 975,
      "y": 1272,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "Kiến trúc HeteroSAGE của nhóm:\n\nLayer 1 (SAGEConv) -- 384d -> 256d\n  (user, reviews, item)  aggregation\n  (item, rev_reviews, user)  reverse edges\n  (item, also_bought, item)  item-item graph\n  W&B: Adam lr=1e-3, 8 epochs\n\nLayer 2 (SAGEConv) -- 256d -> 256d\n  3 loại edge types tương tự\n  -> Final 256d embeddings\n\nDecoder: DotProduct(z_user, z_item) = logit\nLoss: BCEWithLogitsLoss",
      "originalText": "Kiến trúc HeteroSAGE của nhóm:\n\nLayer 1 (SAGEConv) -- 384d -> 256d\n  (user, reviews, item)  aggregation\n  (item, rev_reviews, user)  reverse edges\n  (item, also_bought, item)  item-item graph\n  W&B: Adam lr=1e-3, 8 epochs\n\nLayer 2 (SAGEConv) -- 256d -> 256d\n  3 loại edge types tương tự\n  -> Final 256d embeddings\n\nDecoder: DotProduct(z_user, z_item) = logit\nLoss: BCEWithLogitsLoss",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 500032,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 500033,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": null,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": "model_arch_box",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "tech_stack",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 1502,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 18,
      "text": "Tech Stack: PyTorch + PyG (torch-geometric) | sentence-transformers (all-MiniLM-L6-v2) | scikit-learn | pandas",
      "originalText": "Tech Stack: PyTorch + PyG (torch-geometric) | sentence-transformers (all-MiniLM-L6-v2) | scikit-learn | pandas",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#64748b",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
